# git integration
## 🔹 jenkins pipeline — checkout git
we will learn how to **checkout a git repository** and list files.

pipeline {
    agent any
    stages {
        stage('checkout') {
            steps {
                git branch: 'main', url: 'git@github.com:dec2025_kishore.git'
            }
        }
        stage('list files') {
            steps {
                sh 'ls -la'
            }
        }
    }
}

## 🔹 gitlab ci — checkout 
we will learn how to **checkout a git repository in gitlab ci**.

stages:
